Kmer analysis

Gabe Mednick

7/30/2021

Description of requirements for kmer counting tool

Created a tool to quantify the abundance of every kmer in 8 different experiments.

Requirements for the program are:
1. It intakes FASTA files from a directory
2. It intakes a value k for the size of kmer to evaluate
3. It returns one file per input FASTA with the count of each kmer in that FASTA file, sorted from most to least abundant
4. It returns a warning if any bases beside A, C, T, or G are observed in the input FASTA file
